claim.claim-text:
7. A display control method performed in an image forming apparatus including a display section and an operation section for executing a printing based on setting information of a job, the method comprising the steps of:
displaying a job schedule screen having a time axis, in the job schedule screen two or more job images being displayed along the time axis and each of the job images representing the job;
changing a time scale of the time axis of the job schedule screen by the operation section;
controlling the display section to overlap the job images displayed in the job schedule screen when the time scale of the time axis is changed in the changing step; and
enabling the display section to select each of the overlapped job images displayed in the job schedule screen.
